<br>
Now because the mages didn´t had any great problems themselves they thought about nerfing another class instead of trying a indirect approach. Remember all the crying, bitching and whining when the mod rod change was announced? I have some of those highly intelligent posts saved on my HD if really anyone needs to read them again. Back then you were trying to bitching that other classes should look after themselves and not after the poor, poor mages. Right now you´re bored or whatever and do exactly the same: You look how other classes are doing, see that one class in particular is able to solo and get exp (who wasn´t able to do so) and therefore you simply justify making a silly whine thread on a <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>mage</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> board about getting enchanter SPELLS nerfed instead of concentrating on the real problem:<br>
<br>
SoE is making it just too easy. Don´t concentrate on the class - just ask that certain mobs are made harder, see invisble, are made uncharmable. This will maintain Charm-Usefullness in groups AND raids because some actually do rely on these abilities...<br>
<br>
There is indeed a problem with charm, but it is not the spell itself, it´s the game enviroment that makes it so easy too abuse it. To be honest it is rather disgusting to see some people who were preaching peace during our mod rod crisis (if there ever really was one - at least i didn´t see one, heh) now mutating to some kind of Allknowing SuperMages who have nothing better to do than start a mini war against another class. <p><center><a href= "http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=3300" ><img src = "http://homepage.ruhr-uni-bochum.de/Michael.Kusnierz/Everquest/Pictures/blind.jpg"></a></center></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#333333>- </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower>The Magician's Tower</a><font color=#333333> - </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32>Class Balance</a> <font color=#333333> - </font><a href="http://www.magecompendium.com/">The Mage Compendium</a><font color=#333333> - </font>  <br><br><table border=0 align=center><tr><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">Upgrade your account to ezSupporter...</a></td><td><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/image/spacer.gif" width=15 height=1 border=0></td><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">...and never see another ad or pop-up again</a></td></tr></table><CENTER><!-- START BOTTOM AD SCRIPT -->
